b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Murf AI is best suited for corporate presentations, e learning voiceovers, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Suno, meanwhile, shines for creating music without instruments, content creators needing custom music, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2020, Murf AI describes itself as \"Professional AI voiceovers for enterprise content.\" Suno, established in 2023, positions itself as \"Create full songs with AI from a text prompt.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Suno** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0), more competitive pricing, availability of a free plan. However, this does not mean Murf AI is a poor choice — far from it. Murf AI excels in its own right, particularly for corporate presentations and e learning voiceovers.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value incredibly easy to use, go with Suno. If professional voice quality matters more to you, Murf AI is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
